00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:39.280
"Beri tahu saya."

00:04:39.640 --> 00:04:42.240
"Tolong beritahu aku."

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:47.720
"Tunjukkan aku jalan keluar. Jadikan aku
tangguh untuk menanggung kesedihanku."

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:50.520
"Kembalilah padaku."

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:53.400
"Kembalilah padaku."

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:56.160
"Jangan pergi."

