Laksmi!  Resi!

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.320
Laksmi!

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:14.600
Laksmi!  Resi!

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:42.560
Bibi, tempatnya besar.
